{"tid":2452362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞城槍案未排除種族作祟 美國下半旗 拜登見亞裔領袖","createTime":"2021-03-18T20:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T06:47:29.000Z","uid":105798,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"73ff97fa7b054c83dae5fe39604039bb2398c40f","tid":2452362,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T20:11:06.000Z","msg":"亞特蘭大16日發生連續槍擊案，8名受害者中有6名亞裔，警方至今並未排除是種族偏見引起。總統拜登與副總統賀錦麗19日前往亞特蘭大的行程，將暫停政治活動，改為會見亞裔美國人領袖，討論對亞裔族群的持續攻擊與威脅。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會上周通過1.9兆美元的新冠紓困法案，拜登原定前往亞特蘭大宣傳此事；卻發生嚴重槍擊案，<span class=\"red\">白宮18日宣布，為悼念罹難者，拜登下令所有聯邦機構、軍事基地下半旗5天</span>，直到22日日落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121468/5328545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121468%2F5328545&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSvrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=032a8456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121468/5328545</a>"},{"pid":"ecf0c03b5fcac19ce59483253c90142d4fcb3b34","tid":2452362,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T20:11:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/POTUS/status/1372636991683239946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPOTUS%2Fstatus%2F1372636991683239946&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSvrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=1643c1ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPOTUS%2Fstatus%2F1372636991683239946&h=1237616c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/POTUS/status/1372636991683239946</a>"},{"pid":"dfaa7c7893e4b7a17403654a1ee3bc5a7b242c83","tid":2452362,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T20:12:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/VP/status/1372368895756091401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVP%2Fstatus%2F1372368895756091401&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSvrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=2514bd4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg